{"tid":1667990,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"視700球紀錄如浮雲 C朗：獎杯才是目標","createTime":"2019-10-21T18:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T18:03:50.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"794613b348b7c516945ed9a3748be2ef99480c2f","tid":1667990,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:02:14.000Z","msg":"基斯坦奴朗拿度早前射入自己職業生涯第700球，但對於這個里程碑他未有看得太重，直言入球紀錄遠不如為球隊爭取錦標重要。<br />\n<br />\n早前C朗拿度為葡萄牙出戰國際賽時射入第700球，近日他被傳媒訪問時直言自己未有太著重這個成就：「我沒有想大多700球的事，這已經過去了。我更希望為球隊爭勝，這才是最重要。在場上我最希望幫助球隊，當然我為射入700球而自豪，但目前祖雲達斯的成績才是我首要考慮。只要球隊成績好，紀錄就自然會來。」<br />\n<br />\nC朗職業生涯分別為曼聯及皇家馬德里贏得歐聯，相信他未來的主要任務就是助「老婦人」爭取成為歐洲盟主。（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNtMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=1487ed99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）"},{"pid":"7685198f75e6e49ec84d3080e16d9e6eaa272e88","tid":1667990,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/4e39bac20a07741a9fe0c01bee7c6ff5/tumblr_pznlv46ds21r30r4xo1_500.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F4e39bac20a07741a9fe0c01bee7c6ff5%2Ftumblr_pznlv46ds21r30r4xo1_500.gifv&h=8b2c30d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/aa098de311ba9b40234b7f0862a79f9d/tumblr_pznlv46ds21r30r4xo2_500.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Faa098de311ba9b40234b7f0862a79f9d%2Ftumblr_pznlv46ds21r30r4xo2_500.gifv&h=81ac4ad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/bb911c09fe1b46c30e97b693441a7df5/2d4c6843d8b15f1b-4b/s500x750/dc571f6038d9601e81ce94495d9cb79c3b3292f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fbb911c09fe1b46c30e97b693441a7df5%2F2d4c6843d8b15f1b-4b%2Fs500x750%2Fdc571f6038d9601e81ce94495d9cb79c3b3292f6.jpg&h=0806bdff&s={SIZE}\" />"}]